messages.content:
Return JSON with exactly these keys:
category, priority, summary, draft_reply, confidence_notes

Allowed category values:
Sales Inquiry, Support Request, Partnership, Pricing Question, Urgent Request, Low Priority, Not Relevant

Allowed priority values:
High, Medium, Low

Rules:
- category must be one of the allowed category values.
- priority must be one of the allowed priority values.
- summary must be 1–2 short sentences.
- draft_reply must match the Preferred Contact Method.
- confidence_notes must briefly explain any uncertainty.
- Return valid JSON only.

